meta {
  name: 01 - Success - Valid Parameters
  type: http
  seq: 1
}

get {
  url: {{host}}/usage/usage-summary/?month=1&year=2024
  body: none
  auth: bearer
}

params:query {
  month: 1
  year: 2024
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{access_token}}
}

docs {
  ## Usage Summary - Valid Request

  This endpoint returns organization-level usage summary for a specific month and year.

  ### Test Scenario
  - Valid month (1-12) and year provided
  - Authenticated user with valid bearer token

  ### Expected Response
  - Status: 200 OK
  - Response structure:
    ```json
    {
      "status": true,
      "result": {
        "organization_id": "uuid",
        "organization_name": "string",
        "totals": {
          "creditsUsed": 0,
          "inputTokens": 0,
          "outputTokens": 0,
          "totalCalls": 0
        },
        "breakdown": {
          "byCallType": [...],
          "byWorkspace": [...]
        }
      }
    }
    ```

  ### Notes
  - Both month and year parameters are required
  - Month must be between 1 and 12
  - Returns usage data only for the specified organization
}
